Uncover a mystery and save a town from a curse in 1 Moment of Time: Silentville! Once upon a time in a small, undistinguished town of Silentville people started disappearing - one by one. Even the visitors suddenly disappeared without a trace. Airplanes and birds, trains and pedestrians, drivers, tourists and even bicyclers - all of them have vanished! Will you be able to solve the mystery and release Silentville from its cursed non-existence? 

Beautiful graphics
Original mini-games
Intriguing story

